        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2981526291" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6739310245243659151">The eight plays in <i>Fool for Love and Other Plays</i> make a strong case that Sam Shepard was blessed beyond being tall and handsome with an enviable head of lasting hair. If you are the begrudging type, leave this book and the man’s legacy beyond it alone.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


