      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/trivia/work/200611-fool-for-love-and-other-plays">Trivia About Fool for Love and...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
